channel.title: Im back, i need a little help
channel.description:
New question Well i recently downloaded Ambitionz V1.0, looks good and what i want.. But when i log in it says cant connect to server? old question:
Hey guys, i quit server coding like two years ago, and also runescape. I just got bored, and remembered this place. suprised its stil going strong! :D Anyway, i want to get back into it, does anyone know the name of a server thats not been edited what so ever, but has the new runescape layout (like chat box n stuff) With working clan chat, working animations... so on, but wildy fighting is allowed? Is there such things now? Thanks.

item.title: Im back, i need a little help
item.dc:creator: @jamessemple jamessemple
item.description:
@jamessemple wrote:

[quote=“kantor901, post:9, topic:310182”][quote author=TabbyKiller link=topic=406621.msg3004766#msg3004766 date=1256303185]

So now you must port forward to make a server?

I did port forward… years ago.

Cant remember what my port thingy was though lol =\

You set your ip correct?
Also the portfowarding might be a bit different. Have a look at the tutorial on the tutorials section
[/quote]

Ok ill do that, but here is what it comes up with atm:

Here is as much info as i can give…

When i blick “build”

it comes up with:

“note: Some imput files use or override a deprecated API.
note: Recompile with -Xlint:deprication for details.
Press any key to contine…”

And when you press enter it just goes off.

Could it be clarifying what your saying?[/quote]
on a shorter note, that means it compiled with no errors…
